description: Guests have the ability to answer trivia questions from the Star Wars universe by asking Alexa to “Start Star Wars Quiz” Guests will answer 5 multiple choice questions by responding with the number that corresponds with the correct answer. For example, for the question, "What color is Darth Vader’s lightsaber?” One, Red. Two, Green. Three, Blue. Four, Purple. The correct answer would be “One”. At the end of each game guests will be given a score to see how well they did.
name: Star Wars Quiz
shortDescription: How well do you know the Star Wars Galaxy? Test your knowledge against trivia questions from Classic Star Wars films as well as The Force Awakens
